    <h1>Should Women Take Creatine?</h1>
    <p class="pg-sub">A registered dietitian's evidence-based answer to the question 60,000+ American women search every month. We reviewed 40+ peer-reviewed studies on creatine in female physiology, performance, and long-term health to give you the complete, honest answer.</p>
    <div class="pg-meta">
      <span>Updated April 2026</span>
      <span>40+ Studies Reviewed</span>
      <span>Registered Dietitian Authored</span>
    </div>
  </section>

