    <h2>What Form of Creatine Should Women Take?</h2>

    <p>The choice between powder, capsules, and gummies is mostly about lifestyle fit, not efficacy. All three formats deliver creatine monohydrate to your muscles equivalently when matched for dose. The decision comes down to convenience, cost, and compliance — and compliance is the variable that matters most because creatine only works if you take it consistently.</p>

